<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/mindful/index">List of events (index)</a>
    <br>
    <h1>Today's Date: <%= mindful.date %></h1>
    <h2>How are you feeling today?<br> <%= mindful.beforeActivity %></h1>
    <p>What activity di you do to help ground you? <%= mindful.name %></p>
    <p>How did you feel after your activity? <%= mindful.afterActivity %></p>
    <p>How much water have you drank today? <%= mindful.water %></p>
    <p>How much sleep did you get last night? <%= mindful.sleep %></p>
    <p>Can you recall one positive thing that happened today? <%= mindful.positiveEvent %></p>
    <br>
    <a class="showEdit" href="/mindful/<%=mindful.id %>/edit">Edit</a>
    <br>
    <br>
    <form class="delete" action="/mindful/<%= mindful.id %>?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
        <input class="deleteButton" type="submit" value="DELETE">
    </form>
</body>
</html>